    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.53) - (v2 + 0.59 - v2 + 0.76)) / wp.cos(0.30))
    v0 = 0.55
    v1 = (v0 / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.19) - (tmp + 0.60 / tmp + 0.74)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.98 - v0 + 0.38) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.17)))
